Description: Pythonic ctypes wrapper for libdatovka (Czech ISDS Data Boxes)
 This library provides a small, high-level Python API on top of
 libdatovka, the C client library for the Czech ISDS ("Datove schranky" /
 Data Box) system. It loads libdatovka.so via ctypes at runtime -- no
 compiled extension.
 .
 Covers session login/logout, listing received and sent messages,
 fetching a full message with its attachments, and marking a message
 as read.
